courses.subject: Choose One
courses.customDesc:
Choose one of the following: ANT201, GEOG150, or Lower-Division Social Sciences Course.

Courses from the following disciplines will be acceptable towards the lower-division Social Sciences course: Anthropology, Ethnic Studies, Geography, Sociology, Political Science, Psychology, or Women's, Gender, and Queer Studies.

courses.subject: Approved Elective
courses.customDesc:
Any Approved Elective course can go here.

Options include: POLS285, POLS324, POLS325, POLS332, POLS339, POLS384, POLS386 or POLS387, POLS425, POLS435, POLS451, POLS452; POLS/RELS380, any unused course in concentration.

Consultation with faculty advisor is recommended. A total of 4 units of either POLS386 or POLS387 may connt toward concentration requirements.
